{"tid":368533,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁烈唯拍劇遭車撞 3救護員圍住急救","createTime":"2017-08-21T15:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T17:04:17.000Z","uid":17496,"like":185,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aae632e7a6a1202d8dd00066153153cf250770c6","tid":368533,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"藝人梁烈唯拍網劇期間意外遭車撞傷。有目擊者報料稱，晚上8時許，梁烈唯與吳卓羲於灣仔摩利臣山道拍攝《飛虎極戰》，其間拍攝一個撞車鏡頭時，梁烈唯意外遭私家車撞傷，他受傷躺卧地上，工作人員見狀報案。目擊者提供救護員到場的相片，可見數名救護員替梁烈唯進行急救，據知梁烈唯已送往律敦治醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》晚上致電梁烈唯及其經理人，惟沒有人接聽，而記者用WhatsApp查問事件時，兩人均已讀不回。<br />\n<br />\n梁烈唯於1小時前曾在上址拍攝場地用IG貼文，放上一張自拍相，並留言稱「非常的熱」。上月20日梁烈唯亦曾遇車禍，他駕車收工期間，途經將軍澳環保大道遭後方車輛撞上其車尾，拉傷頸及腰，事後自拍戴頸箍入院相放上fb。<br />\n<br />\n《飛虎極戰》是邵氏兄弟及優酷共同製作的時裝警匪網劇，由苗僑偉(三哥)、王敏德、黃宗澤(Bosco)、吳卓羲、陳凱琳、高海寧等主演<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170821&amp;guid=57110279&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170821%26guid%3D57110279%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=tixlDIhp708RpPAu63cKmwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cafc91a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170821%26guid%3D57110279%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=831760ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170821&amp;guid=57110279&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb391c8b2ff35f9f0343fba6947d761637c095b0","tid":368533,"uid":108170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=